MICRO is a full-service contract manufacturer that draws on over 70 years of experience in medical assembly, precision metal stamping, insert and injection molding, machining, sharpening, finishing, and assembly to deliver the highest quality products to customers in many industries including medical device, automotive, aerospace, and electronics. A truly global company, we manufacture and distribute our products to customers around the world.
